Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.53,0:00:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行星…被吞噬了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.62,0:00:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能死在这种地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.99,0:00:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.91,0:00:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候肯定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 说了一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.52,0:02:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你 兰华
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好了让今天成为Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是让整个银河历史都被改写的一天的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七濑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢卡同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点话要说 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么说 和兰华他们失去联络了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:03:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 米歇尔前辈肯定准时赶到了那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.43,0:03:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 一定没问题的 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 兰华
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道自己这是乱来到什么地步吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是常常说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不如迎头直上 全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后一定会因为没有能表达心意而后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知从什么时候开始眼神变得这么成熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子会在某一天突然变成女人的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你这么说真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经有觉悟的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你开始照料她的那天开始就已经想到会有这么一天的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟……吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人还真是麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使被你这么说我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么说 凯茜中尉和奥兹马少校曾经交往过咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这已经是以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 莫尼卡原来不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你落伍啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种说法也太老了 米娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勃比大尉的心上人不是奥兹马少校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我可以吗？」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「但奥兹马是异性恋」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不过至少可以作为我放在心底里的恋人」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那种追求回报的幼稚的爱情 我早就超越了」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太深奥了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过对我来说果然还是希望我喜欢的人也能喜欢我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就赶紧告白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长在妻子去世后 一直过得很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定非常寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你们都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有发觉的只有舰长一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.73,0:05:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在说我什么事情没有发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我吃一个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请 请用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味 味道如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会成为一个好妻子的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正面宙域中 确认有大量的Defold反应
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.77,0:06:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有了什么消息的话 请联系我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七濑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Macross Frontier政府紧急通知
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在向全舰发布避难警报
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.04,0:06:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人数量正在计算中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数量还在不断增加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.19,0:06:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母舰也有若干
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是敌方的大军
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么现在出现在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们有通过Fold通讯波来确定相互间位置的习性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们可能是被通讯波引到这里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢卡同学也要去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早乙女同学和米歇尔同学都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢卡同学一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能回来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些话想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢卡同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会 保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.39,0:08:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫尼卡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.19,0:08:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的阵形是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将母舰置于后方中心位置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展开鱼鳞阵前进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.42,0:08:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是背水之阵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们绝不让一个敌人穿过防卫线
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰——变形
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.56,0:08:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作快 奈奈 卡娜丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了 爱迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也行 我也行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.29,0:09:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骷髅队长呼叫各机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了 西蒙 约哈尼 佩特罗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是向着Frontier的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.69,0:09:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔 雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们留给我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.36,0:09:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.46,0:09:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙还没宽广到能容下两种生物共存
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我 兰华
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钻石队长呼叫各机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始攻击敌防御线
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为老一套能一直奏效
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些 虫子!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.98,0:10:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 米歇尔 振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔
