Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第一八九队 处于崩溃状态
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Elf 7 请回答 Elf 7
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前双方不分上下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能适用「新统合宪章」中关于特别事项的规定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能许可使用反应武器的话 或许能打开局面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说要展开全面战争吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总统 请下决断
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起课程
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骷髅2号机  米歇尔前辈?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪露小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:11:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不认输
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七濑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骷髅4号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露特前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:12:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到大家的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事太好了 雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 感觉差点被甩走 总算挺过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰华呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:13:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Frontier后方(6,4)位置  发现大量De-fold反应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高能量反应 攻击来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斥力场   最大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:19.52,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(882,964)}Repulsive Field
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.51,0:14:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主岛遭到直接攻击 环境维持系统最大输出 切为最优先模式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艘船?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说兰华也在里面?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诱饵作战?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:15:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能 就凭这些无脑的低等生物?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非Vajra的智能所能及的 这有组织性的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 一定有发出命令的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对吗
