Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标 敌超大型母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰华在那家伙里面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.52,0:15:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露特准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰华她?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.06,0:15:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请向我下达营救的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露特准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:16:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,允许使用Armored-Pack以及反应弹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我方的进攻不会减弱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们见识一下你的实力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露特 一定要无事归来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我保证 绝不死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会带着兰华回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骷髅1号 向骷髅4号通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后我再听理由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰华要是有三长两短的话 我把你轰至渣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delta 1向各机通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:17:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方敌机大量接近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.84,0:17:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的事
